#  FwGuardian 5.0 (2014)
#
#  Interface settings
#  - Set *auto* value to preserve the default value
#  - You can configure VLANs if exist vconfig tool
#  - You can configure IRQ Affinity (CPUs)
#  - Enable or disable rp_filter|arp_filter per interface
#  - Set a bridge interface: auto (ignore), none (ignore), br0, br(n) or use_vlanid (bridge interface per VID)
#
#   Interface   mac         mtu    vlan      bridge    rp_filter arp_filter qlen   CPUs   IPS DropP2P  Description
#   eth0        auto        auto   1         auto      0         0          5000   6,7    1   1        Local network
#

